rtItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530113\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530113\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mwc1665702671394.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mwc1665702671394.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mwc1665702671394.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mwc1665702671394\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the font, color, and image properties for menus.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__section_srz_n4c_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d567226e50\">Syntax</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">menu</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">umenu(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertiesList</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__section_j35_r4c_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d567226e72\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertiesList</var>—semi-colon delimited list of property-value pairs.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">When a color property is not defined, the Windows default is used.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Menu properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">Property</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">Details</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Font</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Font used for text in menus.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rbw1665702850998.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rbw1665702850998.html\" title=\"Name of a logical font to be used for menus, as specified in the initialization file. If not specified, the Windows system default font is used.\">Font</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1 mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2 mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n                     Color Properties \n                  </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Background color of drop-down menu and\n\t\t\t\t popup menus. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColorSelect</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Background color of the selected menu\n\t\t\t\t item. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ovj1665702629207.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ovj1665702629207.html\" title=\"Background color of a tab, menu item, or panel button when it has been selected.\">Active Background Color (BackColorSelect)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColorSidebar</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Background color of the sidebar in\n\t\t\t\t drop-down and popup menus. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oam1665702851070.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oam1665702851070.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the sidebar in a menu. Valid value is a web or system color name, or a hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark). If not specified, the Windows system default is used.\">BackColorSidebar</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColorFill</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Style of the background color for the selected\n                     menu item: <code class=\"ph codeph\">flat</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">gradient</code>.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lpd1665702587794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lpd1665702587794.html\" title=\"Determines whether the background color is styled with a flat or gradient color.\">Gradient Fill Style (BackColorFill)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BorderColorSelect</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Color of the border around a selected menu\n\t\t\t\t item. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vyb1665702851141.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vyb1665702851141.html\" title=\"Color of the border around a selected menu item or panel button. Valid value is a web or system color name, or a hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark). If not specified, the Windows system default is used.\">BorderColorSelect</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ForeColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\"> Color of the text in menu items and\n\t\t\t\t separators in menus. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rbp1665702587714.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rbp1665702587714.html\" title=\"Color to use as the foreground (usually the text color).\">Foreground Color (ForeColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ForeColorSelect</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Color of the text when the menu item is\n\t\t\t\t selected. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yvx1665702629417.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yvx1665702629417.html\" title=\"Color of the label text when the widget, tab, or menu item is selected. If not specified, the Foreground Color is used.\">Active Foreground Color (ForecolorSelect)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ForeColorDisabled</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"></code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Color of the text when the menu item is\n\t\t\t\t disabled.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mqi1665702851211.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mqi1665702851211.html\" title=\"Color of the text when a menu item is disabled. Valid value is a web or system color name, or a hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark). If not specified, the Windows system default is used.\">ForeColorDisabled</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1 mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2 mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n                     Image Properties \n                  </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ImgSelect</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Image displayed as the selected menu item.\n\t\t\t\t </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"daw1665702633024.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/daw1665702633024.html\" title=\"The image that is displayed when the button, tab, or menu item is selected.\">Active Image (ImgSelect)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ImgSidebar</span>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"></code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Image displayed as the side bar of a\n\t\t\t\t drop-down or popup menu. Overrides the <span class=\"keyword\">BackColorSidebar</span> property. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qsr1665702851284.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qsr1665702851284.html\" title=\"Name of the image file or glyph to use as the background of the menu sidebar.\">ImgSidebar</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ImgSize</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__2\">Size used to display an image in front of\n\t\t\t\t the menu item. Uniface always reserves an area in front of a menu item for an image. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17543e1_d17544e1_d17545e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pjz1665702630239.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pjz1665702630239.html\" title=\"Defines the size used to display an icon in widgets and menu items, when both an image and text are defined for the value. Valid values are IMG_SMALL (default), IMG_MEDIUM, IMG_LARGE, IMG_XLARGE, or IMG_NONE.\">Image Size (ImgSize)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__table_d17549e1_d17550e1_d17551e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ila1665702671184.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ila1665702671184.html\" title=\"The [application] section of the initialization file enables you to set application-level defaults for a Windows desktop application.\">[application]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__section_nh2_lpc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d567226e473\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Menu</span> setting control the appearance of menus in the application\n        using colors or images.</p>\n<div class=\"note tip note_tip\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__note_w2861ab1b5b5b5_w2862ab1b5b5_w2863ab1b5_w2864ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Tip:</span> Colors have a performance advantage over images.</div>\n<div class=\"note important note_important\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__note_xfk_tpc_xvb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Important:</span> Using the\n        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Menu</span> setting bypasses the Windows theme manager, so you need to\n      explicitly specify all the properties you want to control. For each color property that is not\n      defined in the property string, the system-defined color is used, which gives menus a flat\n      appearance. You can use the BackColorFill property\n      to set the default to a <code class=\"ph codeph\">gradient</code> fill.</div>\n<p class=\"p\">If menu item definitions specify images (displayed as icons in front of the text), these\n        are only displayed if at least one menu property is set in the application\n          <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">;usys.ini\n[application]\nMenu = umenu(backcolor=control)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">It is advisable to define a font in the property string. If there is no font defined, the\n        current Font0 is used to calculate the size of the menu. If this is changed, the menu size\n        may become bigger or smaller than expected.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">Menu=umenu(font=monomedium;backcolor=blue)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__section_sm3_n2v_cdc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d567226e515\">Example: Setting Menu Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example sets the font, foreground, background, and selection colors for\n        menus. (For readability, this example is formatted over several lines.)</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__pre_q1s_p2v_cdc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">menu=umenu(font=SansMedium;\n backcolor=#fdfdfd;forecolor=black;forecolorselect=green;\n backcolorselect=#c0ddfc;bordercolorselect=#3399ff)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__fig_d144554e1_d144555e1_d144556e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Result</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Result of menu properties\" class=\"image\" id=\"mwc1665702671394__image_gvp_dqc_xvb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/enhancedmenu1.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530113\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530113\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Menu Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the font, color, and image properties for menus. Syntax menu { = } umenu( PropertiesList ) Arguments PropertiesList —semi-colon delimited list of property-value pairs. When a color property is not defined, the Windows default is used. Table 1. Menu properties Property Description Details Font Font used for text in menus. Font Color Properties BackColor Background color of drop-down menu and popup menus. Background Color (BackColor) BackColorSelect Background color of the selected menu item. Active Background Color (BackColorSelect) BackColorSidebar Background color of the sidebar in drop-down and popup menus. BackColorSidebar BackColorFill Style of the background color for the selected menu item: flat or gradient . Gradient Fill Style (BackColorFill) BorderColorSelect Color of the border around a selected menu item. BorderColorSelect ForeColor Color of the text in menu items and separators in menus. Foreground Color (ForeColor) ForeColorSelect Color of the text when the menu item is selected. Active Foreground Color (ForecolorSelect) ForeColorDisabled Color of the text when the menu item is disabled. ForeColorDisabled Image Properties ImgSelect Image displayed as the selected menu item. Active Image (ImgSelect) ImgSidebar Image displayed as the side bar of a drop-down or popup menu. Overrides the BackColorSidebar property. ImgSidebar ImgSize Size used to display an image in front of the menu item. Uniface always reserves an area in front of a menu item for an image. Image Size (ImgSize) Default value: None File section: [application] Description Use the Menu setting control the appearance of menus in the application using colors or images. Tip: Colors have a performance advantage over images. Important: Using the Menu setting bypasses the Windows theme manager, so you need to explicitly specify all the properties you want to control. For each color property that is not defined in the property string, the system-defined color is used, which gives menus a flat appearance. You can use the BackColorFill property to set the default to a gradient fill. If menu item definitions specify images (displayed as icons in front of the text), these are only displayed if at least one menu property is set in the application .ini file. For example: ;usys.ini [application] Menu = umenu(backcolor=control) Copy It is advisable to define a font in the property string. If there is no font defined, the current Font0 is used to calculate the size of the menu. If this is changed, the menu size may become bigger or smaller than expected. Menu=umenu(font=monomedium;backcolor=blue) Copy Example: Setting Menu Properties The following example sets the font, foreground, background, and selection colors for menus. (For readability, this example is formatted over several lines.) menu=umenu(font=SansMedium; backcolor=#fdfdfd;forecolor=black;forecolorselect=green; backcolorselect=#c0ddfc;bordercolorselect=#3399ff) Copy Figure 1. Result Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}